stations <- occ %>%
  group_by(decimalLongitude, decimalLatitude) %>%
  summarize(records = n())

world <- ne_countries(country = "indonesia", scale = "large", returnclass = "sf")

ggplot() +
  geom_sf(data = world, fill = "#000000", color = "#000000") +
  geom_point(data = stations, aes(x = decimalLongitude, y = decimalLatitude), size = 0.5, color = "#cc3300") +
  coord_sf() + ggtitle("OBIS occurrence records in Indonesia") + map_theme

ggplot(occ %>% filter(kingdom == "Animalia")) +
  geom_histogram(aes(x = date_year, fill = phylum), binwidth = 2) + theme_wsj()
